UPON CAREFUL REVIEW OF THE ORIGINAL RETURN, IT WAS DISCOVERED AN INADVERTENT MISTAKE IN THE RESPONSE TO QUESTIONS 13. IN THE ORIGINAL RETURN FILING, IT WAS ERRONEOUSLY CHECK "NO" INSTEAD OF THE CORRECT "YES" BOX. AS THE FOUNDATION DID COMPLY WITH THE PUBLIC INSPECTION REQUIREMENTS. WE UNDERSTAND THE IMPORTANCE OF ACCURATE AND TRUTHFUL REPORTING AND ARE NOW AMENDING THE RETURN TO REFLECT THE CORRECT ANSWER.
